plot: Aliens attack National City with the intention of collecting a large bounty put out on Supergirl.

A large bounty is put out on Supergirl and aliens from far and near attack National City intent on taking out the woman of steel. Alex and Maggie run into Maggie's ex-girlfriend, Emily, who is in town for a week. Hank gets an interesting order from President Marsdin.—sarah_l91
